OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted inquiry says schools
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshould 'self-evaluate'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofsted inspectors should not be in     
OL,6, classrooms and the whole system needs  
OL,7, "a big change", an inquiry has said.   
OL,9,FThe Beyond Ofsted inquiry, chaired by  
OL,10,Fformer schools minister Lord Jim Knight
OL,11,Fand funded by the National Education   
OL,12,FUnion, called for a "transformational" 
OL,13,Falteration to school inspections.      
OL,15,FThe inquiry recommended that schools   
OL,16,Fshould instead be responsible for their
OL,17,Fown improvement plans.                 
OL,19,FOfsted said inspections are needed to  
OL,20,Fensure a high-quality education.       
